column99:
La Pergola, Tønsberg, Norway, is looking for a cook. 
 Job description 
 
 cook for á-la-carte, chef for Italian pizza (italian kitchen) 
 
 Skills 
 
 At least 4 years of experience in a la carte restaurant or non-heating food making (buffets etc.) or chef diploma 
 Norwegian / Scandinavian or English 
 
 Salary 
 
 depends on of experience. 10 years of experience and diploma NOK 207,59,- pr hour pluss evening extra. 
 Weekend extra. and tip 
 
 Working period 1st of June 2022 (ASAP) until 1st of November 2022. 
 Full time, 154 hours pr. month. 
 We will help finding accommodation. 
 More information 
 Anne Lindstrøm, +47 9062 8072, anne@lapergola.no 
 How to apply? 
 send your application to Anne Lindstrøm at anne@lapergola.no 
 Latest application date is 31.05.2022. 
 (from NAV EURES Norway) 
   
 La Pergola is regognized by warm, unformal and pulsating atmosphere where our guests may enjoy good Italian food. During spring and summer our outdoor seating area is full of life and very busy. 
 Tønsberg is located 90 km. south-west of Oslo by the sea with a charming coastline. The city itself is is the largest in the region. Local international airport, www.torp.no 
 www.lapergola.no
